Candidates should send their application letter, full C.V. with current and expected salary and date of availability to us by clicking "APPLY NOW” for arrangement of an interview. (Please state clearly the position you are applying for)

Job Duty


Handle full range of financial statement audit and taxation independently or with team;
Communicate with clients (local and foreign) to obtain information for performing the auditing duty; and
Assist in performing accounting work and ad hoc assignments.

