Degree holder major in accountancy or related field;
Student member of HKICPA or ACCA;
Minimum 3 years solid working experience for accounting and auditing in CPA firm is preferred. Fewer experience will also be considered as Junior Associate;
Knowledge of financial reporting standards including HKFRSs, HKFRS for Private Entities and SME-FRS and auditing standards;
Experience in handling the audit of MNC and consolidation is preferred;
Good command in written and spoken English and Chinese (Cantonese and Mandarin);
Proficiency in Microsoft Office such as Word and Excel;
Strong analytical and communication stills; and
Willing to learn with positive working attitude.

