5-day work, no overtime work and travelling is expected;
14-day annual leave;
Competitive remuneration package;
Medical benefit;
Year-end bonus; and
Study and exam leave.

Interested parties please send full resume with contact details, date of availability, present and expected salary (application without stating these details may not be considered) to us for arrangement an interview.

All information provided by applicants will be treated confidential and used only for recruitment purpose.

